.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-2::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, skateboarding, cycling, sailing
4 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble, backgammon, canasta
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, goldfish
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, roller, scooter, skateboard
 1. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1
 2. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
 3. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's sport is rowing##1
 4. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5
 5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 6. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person playing monopoly is between the person playing canasta and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
 8. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
 9. the owner of the dog is the person playing canasta##1
10. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5
11. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |      4       |
| Sport      | skateboarding       | rowing | sailing     | cycling     |
| Game   | scrabble      | monopoly       | canasta | backgammon |
| Pet           | frog       | goldfish    | dog     | bird         |
| Transport     | skateboard | scooter     | car     | roller       |

