The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, march, october, june
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
 3. the fan of blues is somewhere to the right of the fan of hip-hop##5
 4. the fan of techno is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##5
 5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is between the fan of techno and the fan of rock##2
 7. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is in an even position##4
10. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
11. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who's birthday is in may##1
12. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |    4    |
