 1. the person who growsorchid is somewhere to the left of the firefighter##5
 2. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the writer##1
 3. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
 4. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
 5. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
 6. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
 7. the person drinking mirinda is between the person who growsaconite and the person drinking sprite##2
 8. the musician is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
10. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
11. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
13. the person who growsaconite is somewhere to the left of the firefighter##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |       3        |      4      |
