 3. the egyptian is in an odd position##4
 4. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
 5. the person who's birthday is in november is the person drinking water##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
 8. the nigerian is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
 9. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
10. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
12. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
13. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
