.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, sprite, water
City: nizza, venice, hamburg, prague
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, purple, fuchsia, white
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, drama, epic
 1. the person who likes white is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to prague##5
 2. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 3. the person who likes aquamarine is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who likes white##2
 4. the person traveling to venice is somewhere to the left of the person who likes white##5
 5. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
 6. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 8. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the right of the person who likes purple##5
 9. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
10. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
11. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
12. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3      |        4        |
| Beverage      | water   | hot-chocolate | iced-tea   | sprite          |
| City          | venice    | prague        | hamburg     | nizza          |
| Color           | purple | fuchsia        | aquamarine | white |
| Movie-Genre   | epic    | adventure     | drama      | disaster        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, water
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, bolivar, vegafina, prince
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, disaster, thriller, zombie
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, azure, turquise, yellow
 1. the person who likes azure is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 3. the prince-smoker is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3
 4. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 5. the bolivar-smoker is between the vegafina-smoker and the person watching zombie movies##2
 6. the person watching thriller movies is in an odd position##4
 7. the vegafina-smoker is the person watching disaster movies##1
 8. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 9. the person who likes turquise is on the left or right of the person who likes azure##3
10. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
11. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the game-smoker##1
13. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person watching thriller movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | water      | hot-chocolate | coffee     |
| Cigar           | prince   | game  | bolivar        | vegafina |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy     | zombie     | thriller      | disaster   |
| Color     | azure | turquise | yellow          | orange     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, lime, tomato, watermelon
4 different games are played: bridge, monopoly, go, chess
4 different pets are kept: rat, pony, frog, lizard
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, gospel, punk, soul
 1. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the right of the owner of the pony##5
 2. the fan of soul is the person eating blueberry##1
 3. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the left of the fan of electronic##5
 4. the person playing bridge is in an even position##4
 5. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 6. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the right of the fan of gospel##5
 7. the person playing go is the owner of the lizard##1
 8. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the person playing bridge##5
 9. the fan of punk is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
10. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the right of the person eating tomato##5
11. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
12. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the person eating tomato##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | blueberry | tomato  | watermelon    | lime       |
| Game           | monopoly  | chess | go | bridge  |
| Pet   | pony    | frog   | lizard  | rat     |
| Music-Genre   | soul      | punk    | gospel        | electronic |

 